# Ignore everything.
*
# This is needed so that the rule below can have an effect.
!*/

# Except this specific directory (relative to .gitignore)
# Note that this intentionally does not include subdirectories (such as traces)
# which are not deterministic.
!sma/rebalancing_qps/**
**/traces
# Only track n1's MMA snapshot as a representative per-cfg example; the
# snapshots for other nodes are still written locally (the asimview tool can
# consume them) but would just bloat the PR.
sma/rebalancing_qps/*_mma_snapshot.json
!sma/rebalancing_qps/*_n1_mma_snapshot.json
# And the readme file.
!README.md
